text: Carl-Gustaf Klerck (28 December 1885 - 29 March 1976) was a Swedish fencer. He competed in the individual and team sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1885 births Category:1976 deaths Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish sabre fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Scania
